metadata.name: Kaching VIP #1
metadata.description: Kaching VIP NFTs are a collection of very limited 420 VIP membership for Kaching users. We are using NFT technology for our membership model to reward all of our early adopters and early believers of our project. Kaching VIP will be the highest tier of our membership program. We will announce the other tier of membership program in the near future with more supply so more people can enjoy the benefits of our marketplace membership.
